The Deadbeats - Mr. Patch the Magical Pirate Clown is having a bad day and it's only going to get worse. After a disastrous birthday party, Mr. Patch is harassed to a breaking point by a group of deadbeats. He wants to teach them a lesson, and what was once all good fun turns into a violent and deadly encounter.

2019
Stars: Travis Mills, Houston Towe, Elizabeth Selby
